Package org.spongepowered.api.map.color

Class MapColorTypes

java.lang.Object
org.spongepowered.api.map.color.MapColorTypes
public final class MapColorTypes extends Object
A pseudo-enum of supported elements on a MapCanvas.

The colors that these represent can be retrieved via the MapColorType.color() method.
